title: Wi Isorni menda bias
lyrics:
Wi Isorni menda bias -2
Fwidwng jwng Nwngni serao
Sibidwng jwng nwngni huda -2
(A)
Papni biban khou garsat nanwi
Thabainai lamayao shrang hwnanwi -2
Lingden jwngkhou jiu dwimayao -2
(B)
Jwngbw jagwn nwngni sibiari
Khamsalini jwng shrang alari -2
Subungni jwng shrang alari -2
